to update the vari and of the var is  not present then it will automatically put that value in all
db.students.updateMany(
            {},
            {$currentDate:{"lastModified":true}}
         )

to replace any value in document and make sure it is  not in required format
 db.students.updateOne(
            {name:"aryan"},
            {$unset:{age:""}}
         )

same with (inc) to increment any value (mul) to multiply any value

min and max value
 db.students.insertOne(
            {name:'ram',},
            {$min:{"weight":20}}
         )
same with max (if value is smaller then min the it will updated,if vlaue is smaller than given then it will updated)


array operation
db.personal.updateOne(
            {_id: ObjectId('695113ad1500b6aea61e2624')},
             {$push:{"hobbies":"coding"}}
         )
to delete
 db.personal.updateOne(
            {_id: ObjectId('695113ad1500b6aea61e2624')},
             {$pop:{"hobbies":1}}
         )
{1: for the last val , -1:for the first value}

to delete specifically
 db.personal.updateOne(
            {_id: ObjectId('695113ad1500b6aea61e2624')},
             {$pull:{"hobbies":"football"}}
         )

to replace any value with existing value
 db.students.replaceOne(
            { _id: ObjectId('69514d62253d191e571e2622')},
            {name:"gogo",age:21,course:"BCA"}
         )
